{"ja497:0.1":"Jataka ","ja497:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja497:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja497:0.4":"1. Matangajataka ","ja497:1.1":"“Kuto nu agacchasi dummavasi, ","ja497:1.2":"Otallako pamsupisacakova; ","ja497:1.3":"Sankaracolam patimunca kanthe, ","ja497:1.4":"Ko re tuvam hosi adakkhineyyo”. ","ja497:2.1":"“Annam tavedam pakatam yasassi, ","ja497:2.2":"Tam khajjare bhunjare piyyare ca; ","ja497:2.3":"Janasi mam tvam paradattupajivim, ","ja497:2.4":"Uttitthapindam labhatam sapako”. ","ja497:3.1":"“Annam mamedam pakatam brahmananam, ","ja497:3.2":"Attatthaya saddahato mamedam; ","ja497:3.3":"Apehi etto kimidhatthitosi, ","ja497:3.4":"Na madisa tuyham dadanti jamma”. ","ja497:4.1":"“Thale ca ninne ca vapanti bijam, ","ja497:4.2":"Anupakhette phalamasamana; ","ja497:4.3":"Etaya saddhaya dadahi danam, ","ja497:4.4":"Appeva aradhaye dakkhineyye”. ","ja497:5.1":"“Khettani mayham viditani loke, ","ja497:5.2":"Yesaham bijani patitthapemi; ","ja497:5.3":"Ye brahmana jatimantupapanna, ","ja497:5.4":"Tanidha khettani supesalani”. ","ja497:6.1":"“Jatimado ca atimanita ca, ","ja497:6.2":"Lobho ca doso ca mado ca moho; ","ja497:6.3":"Ete aguna yesu ca santi sabbe, ","ja497:6.4":"Tanidha khettani apesalani. ","ja497:7.1":"Jatimado ca atimanita ca, ","ja497:7.2":"Lobho ca doso ca mado ca moho; ","ja497:7.3":"Ete aguna yesu na santi sabbe, ","ja497:7.4":"Tanidha khettani supesalani”. ","ja497:8.1":"“Kvettha gata upajotiyo ca, ","ja497:8.2":"Upajjhayo ca atha va gandakucchi; ","ja497:8.3":"Imassa dandanca vadhanca datva, ","ja497:8.4":"Gale gahetva khalayatha jammam”. ","ja497:9.1":"“Girim nakhena khanasi, ","ja497:9.2":"ayo dantehi khadasi; ","ja497:9.3":"Jatavedam padahasi, ","ja497:9.4":"yo isim paribhasasi”. ","ja497:10.1":"“Idam vatvana matango, ","ja497:10.2":"isi saccaparakkamo; ","ja497:10.3":"Antalikkhasmim pakkami, ","ja497:10.4":"brahmananam udikkhatam”. ","ja497:11.1":"“Avellitam pitthito uttamangam, ","ja497:11.2":"Bahum pasareti akammaneyyam; ","ja497:11.3":"Setani akkhini yatha matassa, ","ja497:11.4":"Ko me imam puttamakasi evam”. ","ja497:12.1":"“Idhagama samano dummavasi, ","ja497:12.2":"Otallako pamsupisacakova; ","ja497:12.3":"Sankaracolam patimunca kanthe, ","ja497:12.4":"So te imam puttamakasi evam”. ","ja497:13.1":"“Katamam disam agama bhuripanno, ","ja497:13.2":"Akkhatha me manava etamattham; ","ja497:13.3":"Gantvana tam patikaremu accayam, ","ja497:13.4":"Appeva nam putta labhemu jivitam”. ","ja497:14.1":"“Vehayasam agama bhuripanno, ","ja497:14.2":"Pathaddhuno pannaraseva cando; ","ja497:14.3":"Api capi so purimadisam agacchi, ","ja497:14.4":"Saccappatinno isi sadhurupo”. ","ja497:15.1":"“Avellitam pitthito uttamangam, ","ja497:15.2":"Bahum pasareti akammaneyyam; ","ja497:15.3":"Setani akkhini yatha matassa, ","ja497:15.4":"Ko me imam puttamakasi evam”. ","ja497:16.1":"“Yakkha have santi mahanubhava, ","ja497:16.2":"Anvagata isayo sadhurupa; ","ja497:16.3":"Te dutthacittam kupitam viditva, ","ja497:16.4":"Yakkha hi te puttamakamsu evam”. ","ja497:17.1":"“Yakkha ca me puttamakamsu evam, ","ja497:17.2":"Tvanneva me ma kuddho brahmacari; ","ja497:17.3":"Tumheva pade saranam gatasmi, ","ja497:17.4":"Anvagata puttasokena bhikkhu”. ","ja497:18.1":"“Tadeva hi etarahi ca mayham, ","ja497:18.2":"Manopadoso na mamatthi koci; ","ja497:18.3":"Putto ca te vedamadena matto, ","ja497:18.4":"Attham na janati adhicca vede”. ","ja497:19.1":"“Addha have bhikkhu muhuttakena, ","ja497:19.2":"Sammuyhateva purisassa sanna; ","ja497:19.3":"Ekaparadham khama bhuripanna, ","ja497:19.4":"Na pandita kodhabala bhavanti”. ","ja497:20.1":"“Idanca mayham uttitthapindam, ","ja497:20.2":"Tava mandabyo bhunjatu appapanno; ","ja497:20.3":"Yakkha ca te nam na vihethayeyyum, ","ja497:20.4":"Putto ca te hessati so arogo”. ","ja497:21.1":"“Mandabya balosi parittapanno, ","ja497:21.2":"Yo punnakhettanamakovidosi; ","ja497:21.3":"Mahakkasavesu dadasi danam, ","ja497:21.4":"Kilitthakammesu asannatesu. ","ja497:22.1":"Jata ca kesa ajina nivattha, ","ja497:22.2":"Jarudapanamva mukham parulham; ","ja497:22.3":"Pajam imam passatha dummarupam, ","ja497:22.4":"Na jatajinam tayati appapannam. ","ja497:23.1":"Yesam rago ca doso ca, ","ja497:23.2":"avijja ca virajita; ","ja497:23.3":"Khinasava arahanto, ","ja497:23.4":"tesu dinnam mahapphalan”ti. ","ja497:24.1":"Matangajatakam pathamam. "}